nodes.text: The Vos Gesals were a family of singers who became famous in the first clubs and bars of the Uscru Entertainment District of the planet Coruscant. The Vos Gesal Street was named after them, becoming a favorite place for singers, musicians, artists and entertainers. The Vos Gesal Hotel, frequented by actors across the galaxy who visited Coruscant, also shared its name with the family.
